Imbizo-CS Workbench is licensed under the GNU General Public License version 3
or, at your option, any later version.

This project chooses GPLv3-or-later because it protects community access to the
software and improvements while fitting the project model: Imbizo-CS Workbench
is a local desktop application, not a network service. AGPLv3 may be considered
for future server-like components, but such components are out of scope for the
offline-first MVP.

